# Fetched Zig package cache — reproducible from build.zig.zon (URL+hash)
# via `zig build`. Only the hand-vendored nfde source is tracked (it has
# no zon entry; build.zig compiles it directly).
zig-pkg/*
!zig-pkg/nfde/
# Release notes live on the GitHub Releases page, not in-repo.
RELEASE_NOTES_*.md
